As used in this section:
"Agreement" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851;
"Approved company" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851;
"Approved costs" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851;
"Authority" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851;
"Cabinet" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851;
"Secretary" means the secretary of the Tourism, Arts and Heritage Cabinet; and
"Tourism development project" means the same as defined in KRS 148.851.
